title: No. 10 Alabama prepares for tough road against No. 9 Texas A
text:
No. 10 Alabama prepares for tough road against No. 9 Texas A&M Tools By Alabama News Network 
Story Created: Oct 12, 2015 at 6:28 PM CDT 
Tuscaloosa, AL - Alabama head coach Nick Saban spoke to the media Monday during his weekly press conference. Saban previewed the No. 10 ranked Crimson Tide's matchup against the No. 9 ranked Texas A&M Aggies. 
Alabama and Texas A&M kickoff set for 2:30pm CT on CBS.
